Benefits of Online Schooling in India

Future of Education

A new world order post 2020, dictates a whole new outlook at its education system too.

Healthy Balance between Fun & Learning

All work and no play make children dull and dreary. We provide just the right balance between scholastic and co-scholastic areas.

Flexible Learning

Study at a pace that accommodates an absorbent mind. Assimilation is best, when the mind is fresh.

Curated Curriculum

Our curriculum is tailor-made to forge tomorrow’s leaders.

Welcome To Spruha - India’s Best Online School 

A brand-new world order coerces us to think differently and re-think our ways of working, living and educating our future generations.
Welcome to Spruha, the Virtual school!

Spruha, in Sanskrit, denotes the harbinger of ambition and desire.
For your child, we present the right balance of a great learning environment combined with the right values, quintessential life skills and a safe, secure and exciting place to blossom.

We are a 100% online school offering flexible batch timings, choice of subjects, engaging curriculum, competitive fee structure and personalised support to our students, which makes us the first choice as top online schools in India. At Spruha, we are committed to provide our students everything they would get at a traditional school and much beyond….

Our programs are designed at par with international curriculum offering a right balance between scholastic and co-scholastic areas. A focus on accessibility for all to excellent education is the cornerstone of Spruha and will always stay the essence of our beliefs. We lay emphasis on generating love for education among our students and carve joyful learning experiences for them, which has made us the most sought-after and best online school in India.

We have earned a reputation of a leading online school in Bengaluru, Hyderabad, Pune, Delhi, Mumbai and other parts of India. Having students from different parts of the country in one class has helped us in providing culturally rich classroom experiences, thus, strengthening the joy of learning.

Read More
  • Syllabi Offered

We offer curriculum of NIOS, so that you get to pick what is best suited for your children and their needs.

Additional languages available.

  • Subjects Offered

Grades 5, 6, 7, 8 – English, Mathematics, Science & Social Science.
Grades 9, 10 – English, Mathematics, Science,  Social Science, Business Studies, Home Science, Psychology, Indian Culture & Heritage.
Additional languages – Hindi, Kannada, Marathi , Sanskrit can be opted.

  • Co-Scholastic Areas

We cater to the creative needs of all our students and for those interested in performing arts we offer Online coaching in singing, dance and playing musical instruments.

  • Teaching Staff

Onboard Spruha, is by far the best, most competent and most compassionate staff that will accelerate your child’s growth and see that they soar in every endeavour they undertake, be it scholastic and Co-Scholastic areas.

  • Individual Attention

We are committed to providing individual and personalised attention to each of our valued students, which is why we maintain a good student teacher ratio at all times.

  • Timings

There will be 2 Batches :

  • 9 AM – 12:30 PM
  • 4 PM – 7:30 PM  

Our Core Values

Integrity

Integrity is the soul of all virtue.

Compassion

Compassion is the soul of all humanity.

Excellence

Excellence at the heart of all human endeavors.

Why Choose Us ?

Intellectual development

A child blossoms when the mind is free and imagination is left unfettered. We believe in according the right balance of liberty and supervision so that every child experiences holistic development.

Holistic development

We believe that a child’s growth is stimulated in equal measure through studies and games and hence we offer equal opportunities to excel at both.

Optimum utilization of time

Children these days, lead ultra-fast paced, busy lives and every moment is crucial. We ensure engagement that takes this into account and provides the best utilization of their most precious resource: time.

Custom-paced learning

Learning here isn’t by rote, so days are not spent cramming subjects. Instead, every child studies subjects that they wish to and at a pace that best suits them.
